 white jug" title="Christmas gravy recipes" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Collection</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Christmas gravy</h3><div class="vertical-push-item__count"> 10 Recipes</div> </a></article><article id="node-4255431" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/lamb-apricot-shallot-tagine"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src="//www.bbcgoodfood.com/sites/default/files/styles/carousel_medium/public/recipe_images/tagine_1.jpg?itok=W1Wr33Ld" width="468" height="382" alt="Lamb, apricot &amp; shallot tagine" title="Lamb, apricot &amp; shallot tagine" /> <span class="vertical-push-item__badge vertical-push-item__badge--type">Recipe</span></div><h3 class="vertical-push-item__title"> Lamb, apricot &amp; shallot tagine</h3><div class="push-item__ratings"><div class="clearfix fivestar-average-stars fivestar-average-text"><div class="fivestar-static-form-item"><div class="form-item form-type-item"><div class="field-main"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">4.886365</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="description"><p class="fivestar-summary fivestar-summary-">(11 <span class="rating-text"> ratings</span>)</p></div></div></div></div></div> </a></article><article id="node-101948" class="vertical-push-item vertical-push-item--carousel node node-recipe node-large-push-item clearfix"> <a href="/recipes/1759645/braised-beef-with-anchovy-toasts"><div class="vertical-push-item__image"> <img src